Ilyenkov Philosophy Text Archive - Layered Licensing

Copyright (c) 2026 Ilyenkov Philosophy Text Archive contributors

This repository contains materials with different copyright and licensing
statuses. No single license applies to the entire repository.

1. Software

Project-authored code, scripts, tests, schemas, Git hooks, and comparable
software infrastructure are licensed under the MIT License. See
LICENSES/MIT.

2. Project-authored documentation

Project-authored documentation, research notes, and original annotations are
licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
License (CC BY-SA 4.0), unless a file states otherwise. See
LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-4.0.

3. Factual metadata

Project-created factual bibliographic, provenance, source, checksum, and
status metadata are dedicated to the public domain under CC0 1.0 Universal,
unless a file contains third-party expressive content or states otherwise.
See LICENSES/CC0-1.0.

4. Third-party and controlled content

Philosophical source texts, historical and modern translations, scans,
images, transcriptions, and other third-party materials retain their own
copyright and license status. Their presence in this repository does not
place them under the project licenses. Public redistribution is permitted
only when the repository's rights registry explicitly approves the exact
file and checksum.

See RIGHTS.md for the authoritative scope and redistribution policy.
